---
title: Black Bean Pork Mince Noodles with Bell Pepper and Green Beans
description: These Black Bean Pork Mince Noodles are a crowd pleaser and one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/black-bean-pork-mince-noodles-b934bd57-cea436b6.jpg
